#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_ACCEPTGIFT.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_ACCEPTGIFT.1"
msgid "You're just giving this to me? Thanks!"
msgstr "Bunu öylece bana mı veriyorsun? Sağ ol!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_ACCEPTGIFT.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_ACCEPTGIFT.2"
msgid "Wow, I didn't even have to steal it- I mean, thanks!"
msgstr "Vay, çalmama bile gerek kalmadı- yani, sağ ol!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_ACCEPTGIFT.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_ACCEPTGIFT.3"
msgid "They just give you stuff around here? Neat!"
msgstr "Burada öylece eşya mı veriyorlar? Süper!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.1"
msgid "Did you hear that?\nYou don't think we were followed, do you?"
msgstr "Bunu duydun mu?\nTakip edildiğimizi düşünmüyorsun, değil mi?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.2"
msgid "This sure is cozy."
msgstr "Burası epey rahat doğrusu."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.3"
msgid "It's nice to warm your talons by the fire."
msgstr "Pençelerini ateşte ısıtmak güzel."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.4"
msgid "There's been a mysterious murder here...\nAnd with any luck, we'll be back again next year! Cah-cah-cah!"
msgstr "Burada esrarengiz bir cinayet işlenmiş...\nVe biraz şansla, gelecek yıl yine geleceğiz! Gak-gak-gak!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.5"
msgid "I wonder why the featherfree creatures are so scared of the dark?"
msgstr "Tüysüz yaratıklar karanlıktan neden bu kadar korkuyor acaba?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_CAMPFIRE.6"
msgid "Does anyone have some corn?"
msgstr "Mısır olan var mı?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.1"
msgid "Wow! It's so festive!"
msgstr "Vay! Tam şenlik havası!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.2"
msgid "Best Cawnival ever!"
msgstr "Şimdiye kadarki en iyi Karganaval!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.3"
msgid "Last year's Cawnival was not this fancy."
msgstr "Geçen yılki Karganaval bu kadar şatafatlı değildi."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.4"
msgid "I wanna watch the games!"
msgstr "Oyunları izlemek istiyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS.5"
msgid "Have you checked out the Prize Booth yet?"
msgstr "Ödül Tezgahı'na uğradın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS_SNACK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS_SNACK.1"
msgid "If I eat anymore, I'm gonna pop.\nHmm, pop... popcorn... mmmmm..."
msgstr "Daha fazla yersem patlayacağım.\nHmm, patlak... patlamış mısır... mmmmm..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS_SNACK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS_SNACK.2"
msgid "Do you think they're trying to fatten us up and eat us?\nNaw... they don't look that clever."
msgstr "Bizi semirtip yemeye mi çalışıyorlar dersin?\nYok... o kadar zeki görünmüyorlar."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS_SNACK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_LOTS_SNACK.3"
msgid "We're lucky that Corvus found this place."
msgstr "Corvus'un burayı bulması iyi oldu."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.1"
msgid "They must still be setting up."
msgstr "Hâlâ hazırlık yapıyor olmalılar."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.2"
msgid "Where's the party?"
msgstr "Parti nerede?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.3"
msgid "Most boring Midsummer Cawnival ever."
msgstr "Şimdiye kadarki en sıkıcı Yaz Ortası Karganaval'ı."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.4"
msgid "More like Caw-no-val."
msgstr "Daha çok Karga-yok-val."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.5"
msgid "Looks like I got here too early..."
msgstr "Buraya çok erken gelmişim galiba..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE.6"
msgid "I'm gonna tell my friends to wait until there's more set up."
msgstr "Arkadaşlarıma daha çok şey hazırlanana kadar beklemelerini söyleyeceğim."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE_SNACK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE_SNACK.1"
msgid "All this Cawnival fun is making me peckish."
msgstr "Bu Karganaval eğlencesi iştahımı kabarttı."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE_SNACK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE_SNACK.2"
msgid "Those snacks look so good...\nI'm sure they wouldn't mind if I snuck a bite..."
msgstr "O atıştırmalıklar pek güzel görünüyor...\nBir lokma çalsam aldırış etmezler herhalde..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE_SNACK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_NONE_SNACK.3"
msgid "I'm starving after that long trip."
msgstr "O uzun yolculuktan sonra açlıktan ölüyorum."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.1"
msgid "Nicely set up."
msgstr "Güzel hazırlanmış."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.2"
msgid "It's alright... but it could use some flair."
msgstr "Fena değil... ama biraz şıklık eksik."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.3"
msgid "I've seen better Cawnivals."
msgstr "Daha iyi Karganavallar gördüm."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME.4"
msgid "The party is just getting started!"
msgstr "Parti daha yeni başlıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME_SNACK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME_SNACK.1"
msgid "What a fun place, nobody chases us away!"
msgstr "Ne eğlenceli bir yer, kimse bizi kovalamıyor!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME_SNACK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME_SNACK.2"
msgid "Who was that, with the red fur? He seemed kinda familiar."
msgstr "Şu kırmızı tüylü olan kimdi? Sanki bir tanıdık geldi."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME_SNACK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_AMBIENT_SOME_SNACK.3"
msgid "I hope we can have the Cawnival here again next year."
msgstr "Umarım gelecek yıl Karganaval'ı yine burada yaparız."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.1"
msgid "Wow! It's so festive!"
msgstr "Vay! Ne kadar şenlikli!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.2"
msgid "Nicely done."
msgstr "Güzel iş."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.3"
msgid "You must be good at these games."
msgstr "Bu oyunlarda iyi olmalısın."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.4"
msgid "Have you tried Egg Scramble? It's my favorite game!"
msgstr "Yumurta Telaşı'nı denedin mi? En sevdiğim oyun!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.5"
msgid "I watched someone play Hubbub for Grub, and now I'm hungry..."
msgstr "Birinin Yem için Yaygara oynadığını izledim, şimdi de karnım acıktı..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS.6"
msgid "Have you won any prizes yet?"
msgstr "Hiç ödül kazandın mı?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS_SNACK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS_SNACK.1"
msgid "It's nice to rest our wings a little.\nWe usually can't stay in one place too long."
msgstr "Kanatlarımızı biraz dinlendirmek güzel.\nGenelde tek bir yerde fazla kalmayız."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS_SNACK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS_SNACK.2"
msgid "Have you seen the lady that watches the Cawnival at night?\nSquawck about creepy."
msgstr "Geceleri Karganaval'ı izleyen hanımı gördün mü?\nGak desem az gelir, ne ürpertici!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS_SNACK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_LOTS_SNACK.3"
msgid "Are you having fun? I sure am!"
msgstr "Eğleniyor musun? Ben kesinlikle eğleniyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.1"
msgid "You should decorate more."
msgstr "Daha çok süslemen lazım."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.2"
msgid "Where are the decorations?"
msgstr "Süslemeler nerede?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.3"
msgid "It's not a Cawnival without decorations around the Tree!"
msgstr "Ağaç'ın etrafında süsleme olmadan Karganaval olmaz!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE.4"
msgid "This must be your first Cawnival."
msgstr "İlk Karganaval'ın olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE_SNACK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE_SNACK.1"
msgid "Hey, mind sharing your snacks?"
msgstr "Hey, atıştırmalıklarını paylaşır mısın?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE_SNACK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE_SNACK.2"
msgid "Where are we from? Oh you know, here and there..."
msgstr "Nerelerden mi geliyoruz? Ah bilirsin işte, oradan buradan..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE_SNACK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_NONE_SNACK.3"
msgid "You stay here all year?\nWow, not having wings must be tough."
msgstr "Bütün yıl burada mı kalıyorsun?\nVay, kanatları olmamak zor olmalı."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.1"
msgid "You're doing a pretty good job."
msgstr "Oldukça iyi iş çıkarıyorsun."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.2"
msgid "I wish there were more decorations around the Cawnival Tree..."
msgstr "Keşke Karganaval Ağacı'nın etrafında daha çok süsleme olsa..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.3"
msgid "I've seen better Cawnivals. Just saying."
msgstr "Daha iyi Karganavallar gördüm. Söylemiş olayım."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME.4"
msgid "Gotta say, last year's Cawnival was better..."
msgstr "İtiraf etmeliyim, geçen yılki Karganaval daha iyiydi..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME_SNACK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME_SNACK.1"
msgid "So where do YOU come from? Just curious!"
msgstr "Peki SEN nereden geliyorsun? Sadece merak ettim!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME_SNACK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME_SNACK.2"
msgid "I can't believe you'd never seen a Cawnival before we came!\nYou sure were missing out."
msgstr "Biz gelmeden önce Karganaval'ı hiç görmediğine inanamıyorum!\nKesin çok şey kaçırmışsın."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME_SNACK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_DECOR_PLAYER_SOME_SNACK.3"
msgid "You're pretty weird. Has anyone told you that?"
msgstr "Bayağı tuhafsın. Sana hiç söylediler mi?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.1"
msgid "Ooooh someone's playing!"
msgstr "Vaay biri oynuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.2"
msgid "Let's watch the featherfree creature play!"
msgstr "Şu tüysüz mahluk nasıl oynuyor görelim!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.3"
msgid "Look, someone's about to play!"
msgstr "Bak, biri oynamak üzere!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.4"
msgid "I love watching these games!"
msgstr "Bu oyunları izlemeye bayılıyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_GAME_GOTO.5"
msgid "Oooh, that game's my favorite!"
msgstr "Ohoo, en sevdiğim oyun bu!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_HASGIFT.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_HASGIFT.1"
msgid "What's with all the presents? This is starting to feel suspicious..."
msgstr "Ne bu hediye yağmuru? Şüpheli görünmeye başladı..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_HASGIFT.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_HASGIFT.2"
msgid "Thanks, but I've already got something!"
msgstr "Teşekkürler, zaten elimde bir şey var!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_HASGIFT.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_HASGIFT.3"
msgid "Sorry, busy. Maybe try someone else."
msgstr "Kusura bakma, meşgulüm. Belki başka birini denersin."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_OTHERGAME_GOTO.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_OTHERGAME_GOTO.1"
msgid "What kind of game is that?"
msgstr "Bu ne tür bir oyun?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_OTHERGAME_GOTO.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_OTHERGAME_GOTO.2"
msgid "Are the featherfree creatures fighting? I want to watch!"
msgstr "Tüysüz mahluklar dövüşüyor mu? İzlemek istiyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_REFUSEGIFT.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_REFUSEGIFT.1"
msgid "Oh... wow... um, that's okay, you keep it."
msgstr "Aa... vay... ıı, sorun değil, sende kalsın."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_REFUSEGIFT.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_REFUSEGIFT.2"
msgid "Aw, wouldn't ya know it, I'm actually allergic to that exact thing."
msgstr "Aaa, biliyor musun, tam da ona alerjim var."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_REFUSEGIFT.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_REFUSEGIFT.3"
msgid "No thanks, I don't want it."
msgstr "Yok sağ ol, istemiyorum."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.1"
msgid "Caaah!"
msgstr "Gaaak!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.2"
msgid "Time to take off!"
msgstr "Havalanma vakti!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.3"
msgid "The feathers are flying!"
msgstr "Tüyler havada uçuşuyor!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.4"
msgid "No thanks!"
msgstr "Sağ ol istemem!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.5"
msgid "I'm outta here!"
msgstr "Ben kaçtım!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_CROWKID_SCARED.6"
msgid "Scatter!!"
msgstr "Dağılın!!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.1"
msgid "Yes, yes! It's that most wonderful time of year again!"
msgstr "Evet, evet! Yılın o muhteşem zamanı yine geldi!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.2"
msgid "I, the great Goodfeather, have graciously decided to return with my wondrous Cawnival!"
msgstr "Ben, ulu İyitüy, harikulade Karganaval'ımla geri dönmeye lütfetmiş bulunuyorum!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.3"
msgid "You there! How would you like to be a part of something spectacular?!"
msgstr "Hey sen! Muhteşem bir şeyin parçası olmaya ne dersin?!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.4"
msgid "It is I, a merry wanderer with feathers black as night!"
msgstr "Benim, geceler kadar kara tüylü neşeli bir gezgin!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.5"
msgid "I've been known by many names, but you may call me Corvus Goodfeather!"
msgstr "Beni birçok isimle bilirler, ama sen bana Corvus İyitüy diyebilirsin!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.6"
msgid "\"Not yet mid-summer\", you say? Well my friend, the early bird gets the worm!"
msgstr "\"Henüz yaz ortası değil\" mi diyorsun? Eh dostum, erken kalkan kuş solucanı kapar!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.7
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.7"
msgid "Oh lucky, lucky you, to be a stop on our flight of fancy!"
msgstr "Ah ne talihli, ne talihlisin, hayalbaz uçuşumuzun durağı olmak!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.8
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.8"
msgid "Be merry, for good old Goodfeather has returned with his spectacular Cawnival!"
msgstr "Şenlenin, çünkü ihtiyar İyitüy muhteşem Karganaval'ıyla geri döndü!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.9
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_CARNIVAL.9"
msgid "Last year was so profitable- er, FUN, that we just couldn't stay away!"
msgstr "Geçen yıl o kadar kârlı- ee, EĞLENCELİYDİ ki uzak duramadık!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.1"
msgid "The Cawnival is underway!"
msgstr "Karganaval başladı!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.2"
msgid "Welcome, welcome, one and all!"
msgstr "Hoş geldiniz, hoş geldiniz, herkes!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.3"
msgid "Buy your tokens here!"
msgstr "Jetonlarınızı buradan alın!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.4
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.4"
msgid "Enjoy the Cawnival!"
msgstr "Karganaval'ın tadını çıkarın!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.5
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.5"
msgid "Why not purchase a lovely miniature to set under the Tree?"
msgstr "Ağaç'ın altına koymak için sevimli bir minyatür almaya ne dersiniz?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.6
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.6"
msgid "The games look fun, don't they? Why not purchase a token or twelve?"
msgstr "Oyunlar eğlenceli görünüyor, değil mi? Bir veya bir düzine jeton almaya ne dersiniz?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.7
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.7"
msgid "Win tickets, trade tickets for fabulous prizes!"
msgstr "Bilet kazan, biletleri muhteşem ödüllerle takas et!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.8
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.8"
msgid "Take a glance at the Prize Booth, friends! We have spectacular trinkets from far and wide!"
msgstr "Ödül Kulübesi'ne bir göz atın dostlar! Uzak diyarlardan muhteşem ufak tefekler getirdik!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.9
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_ANNOUNCE_GENERIC.9"
msgid "\"Not yet mid-summer\", you say? Well my friend, the early bird gets the worm!"
msgstr "\"Henüz yaz ortası değil\" mi diyorsun? Eh dostum, erken kalkan kuş solucanı kapar!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_BORED.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_BORED.1"
msgid "Oh, I think you nearly scored a point that time!"
msgstr "Aa, sanırım bu sefer sayı yapmaya az kaldı!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_BORED.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_BORED.2"
msgid "Have you never played a Cawnival game before?"
msgstr "Daha önce hiç Karganaval oyunu oynamadınız mı?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_BORED.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_BORED.3"
msgid "Better luck next time, perhaps?"
msgstr "Belki bir dahaki sefere bol şans?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_CHEER.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_CHEER.1"
msgid "Yes, yes! You're a natural!"
msgstr "Evet, evet! Doğuştan yeteneklisiniz!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_CHEER.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_CHEER.2"
msgid "You've got a good grasp of the game, I see!"
msgstr "Görüyorum ki oyunu iyi kavramışsınız!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_CHEER.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_CHEER.3"
msgid "Such an excellent performance! I do hope you purchase more tokens to show us again!"
msgstr "Ne mükemmel bir performans! Umarım bize tekrar göstermek için daha fazla jeton alırsınız!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_BORED.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_BORED.1"
msgid "Too bad. Better luck next time!"
msgstr "Çok yazık. Bir dahaki sefere bol şans!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_BORED.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_BORED.2"
msgid "I have plenty more tokens to sell if you'd like to try again!"
msgstr "Tekrar denemek isterseniz satacak bir sürü jetonum daha var!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_CHEER.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_CHEER.1"
msgid "Well done, well done! Now why don't you go peruse our Prize Booth?"
msgstr "Aferin, aferin! Şimdi Ödül Kulübemize göz atmaya ne dersiniz?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_CHEER.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_GAME_END_CHEER.2"
msgid "What an astonishing display! Here, let old Corvus Goodfeather give you an extra ticket."
msgstr "Ne hayret verici bir gösteri! Bırakın da ihtiyar Corvus İyitüy size fazladan bir bilet versin."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_OTHERGAME_TALK.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_OTHERGAME_TALK.1"
msgid "What is this game?"
msgstr "Bu nasıl bir oyun?"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_OTHERGAME_TALK.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_OTHERGAME_TALK.2"
msgid "What an odd game. Not nearly as fun as the ones we have at the Cawnival!"
msgstr "Ne tuhaf bir oyun. Karganaval'dakilere yaklaşamaz bile!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_OTHERGAME_TALK.3
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_OTHERGAME_TALK.3"
msgid "I'm not familiar with the rules..."
msgstr "Kurallarına aşina değilim..."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_GENERIC.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_GENERIC.1"
msgid "Look here, I have such wonderful games for you to play!"
msgstr "Buraya bakın, oynamanız için harika oyunlarım var!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_GENERIC.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_GENERIC.2"
msgid "A Cawnival is not complete without some fun and games."
msgstr "Bir parça eğlence ve oyun olmadan Karganaval tamamlanmaz."

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_PLAZA.1
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_PLAZA.1"
msgid "Yes, yes! The centerpiece must be set!"
msgstr "Evet, evet! Merkez parça yerleştirilmeli!"

#. STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_PLAZA.2
msgctxt "STRINGS.CARNIVAL_HOST_SELL_PLAZA.2"
msgid "The Cawnival cannot begin until the Tree is planted!"
msgstr "Ağaç dikilmeden Karganaval başlayamaz!"

