#. STRINGS.UI.ACHIEVEMENTS.LAVAARENA.ACHIEVEMENT.laq_axethrow.TITLE
msgctxt "STRINGS.UI.ACHIEVEMENTS.LAVAARENA.ACHIEVEMENT.laq_axethrow.TITLE"
msgid "Chuck It Overboard"
